            "text": "{\n  \"id\": \"resp_06667f4aa8ccbba0006a1503e37e9c8193802cd26bc319fd25\",\n  \"object\": \"response\",\n  \"created_at\": 1779762147,\n  \"status\": \"completed\",\n  \"background\": false,\n  \"billing\": {\n    \"payer\": \"developer\"\n  },\n  \"completed_at\": 1779762151,\n  \"error\": null,\n  \"frequency_penalty\": 0.0,\n  \"incomplete_details\": null,\n  \"instructions\": \"Think carefully before answering.\",\n  \"max_output_tokens\": null,\n  \"max_tool_calls\": null,\n  \"model\": \"gpt-5.4-2026-03-05\",\n  \"moderation\": null,\n  \"output\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"rs_06667f4aa8ccbba0006a1503e3ebd08193b3dffcb3daf4e220\",\n      \"type\": \"reasoning\",\n      \"encrypted_content\": \"gAAAAABqFQPn4Zy43CzyzjY080Z0Aj_0dyGT1fqPkg7prj93E0H88TWzB2FqSTUz-rYK88aoZv_AmZzVhd_RWIzxZe6iKfO9_WoFVK7tcAqpVuflIZjNxkKO5P2H5-GQDPNvBENCqopduOT16cZFFsSsXooN_eY35ejrtjxmOjnlVlAV2OLOJNzsbkNITSCxvZpl51dCDBWl0eZ2gl9QEtuiW0OZ6o-R2roHV-WiCUNWqmlYMJ5sJsHOy2Im1p3IiqZSkStSSmArEXFw20CJdmr1a51bEF9GCrxAAL_O63zGZMIb6T1UnM1MtFOl7ACmvnz2X-IdYfgu32rkaj-kGp4RIHZhxYbpiYAWDaz4FW_NLQOTXk_tnFAOgCT66bfqlcG94wJmd6OvBP9PqcSzNbx44XX1ZXoAECvUg9nT7Z__NFNl3pXfjQnPsRfXU0OmcF5KCSvYwAMcdv5PWWf7Oi4QmWCGkWyHOuYO2syjR8Eov116Vh7BpUA4St__G0NKjUT2J4fvaCpPItUcVHIg3jq6XNL8HR6R67LqOKiMmGFremsUsTDLfRnOfCibNK5h5pc640a1yafo2CCycNgso0AW9lKhJGCiHNnxd4e714-mXacC0Og3p9bUbBn_VgxnKTmrb-lXSfFy5COaL54YD1daqIs1oVMnrf_V28bPpobKCTBU3onGWLlzigl-qdAqGVaQwmbY5VB5XoisuM2jhMWTPwbufUZWLWlcThqISkX89HGHrL_L7yAg-Z4YzS6KT3074zws0hnJLeU6843gGEvRP5pxOh3_mzHS2fL0Iwu_v0WnrHaUv9aTWSMHfc8XTU-CwuChE1LRZcFjw9IQpBm5PW60C31kv7IdTam2fIiY4N44Fd3sdA2_ma-_I6KqyyLzFq6Gmkozlx0mu3i3hL4QuR1UnQ-w4ycEC5IkCkzbEB5X4W_VutT0eoJTJvaWieeECvYRXtQZhK2Z_Wj1tLCc9-mKqeOz923y6UxsNAk1-loq6P0WSrELulVkelzsp22kbJmxEpx1nZ3835hh8T1RM1U9L_6My_JT2B08ccQ701Na3Fh3w9ipdHJLnaqd5x7G9T26chCDf9vq3V_FTu7Cfrd8vj8RRH03lQ2KE7zPhVpRYe6bVt1dJT52P6aC61n5LTAfM3JOC9Knb_h741YwciVRdkhr4mzaYZc61RI_1eDvTJQFkfMUF7e4LyJtB5wmY0G7UkIR\",\n      \"summary\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"summary_text\",\n          \"text\": \"**Calculating average speed**\\n\\nI want to give a clear answer, so I\\u2019m computing some distances first. I\\u2019ve got 120 km at 2.5 hours, which equals 300 km, and then 80 km at 1.75 hours gives me 140 km. Adding those together gives a total distance of 440 km. The total time taken is 4.25 hours. Now, for the average speed, I can divide the total distance by the total time: 440 km divided by 4.25 hours gives me about 103.5 km/h.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"msg_06667f4aa8ccbba0006a1503e75b748193b6323611043ae02c\",\n      \"type\": \"message\",\n      \"status\": \"completed\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"output_text\",\n          \"annotations\": [],\n          \"logprobs\": [],\n          \"text\": \"- Distance in first part: \\\\(120 \\\\times 2.5 = 300\\\\) km  \\n- Distance in second part: \\\\(80 \\\\times 1.75 = 140\\\\) km  \\n\\nTotal distance:\\n\\n\\\\[\\n300 + 140 = 440 \\\\text{ km}\\n\\\\]\\n\\nTotal time:\\n\\n\\\\[\\n2.5 + 1.75 = 4.25 \\\\text{ hours}\\n\\\\]\\n\\nAverage speed:\\n\\n\\\\[\\n\\\\frac{440}{4.25} \\\\approx 103.5 \\\\text{ km/h}\\n\\\\]\\n\\n**Answer:**  \\n- **Total distance:** 440 km  \\n- **Average speed:** 103.5 km/h\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"phase\": \"final_answer\",\n      \"role\": \"assistant\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"parallel_tool_calls\": true,\n  \"presence_penalty\": 0.0,\n  \"previous_response_id\": null,\n  \"prompt_cache_key\": null,\n  \"prompt_cache_retention\": \"in_memory\",\n  \"reasoning\": {\n    \"context\": \"current_turn\",\n    \"effort\": \"high\",\n    \"summary\": \"detailed\"\n  },\n  \"safety_identifier\": null,\n  \"service_tier\": \"default\",\n  \"store\": true,\n  \"temperature\": 1.0,\n  \"text\": {\n    \"format\": {\n      \"type\": \"text\"\n    },\n    \"verbosity\": \"medium\"\n  },\n  \"tool_choice\": \"auto\",\n  \"tools\": [],\n  \"top_logprobs\": 0,\n  \"top_p\": 0.98,\n  \"tru